{"tid":2374430,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[老貓不死] 帝國戰爭博物館有本書講香港貓Simon","createTime":"2021-01-21T08:22:30.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-22T23:37:22.000Z","uid":43150,"like":27,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"4f5c627f8e05350a9c5ea1c931cfbacd1b1a3794","tid":2374430,"uid":43150,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-21T08:22:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/stretching.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />又係我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n各位有仔女嘅巴打，或者準備返英國嘅巴打，有本書推介俾你地，希望冇Wow到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n英國帝國戰爭博物館(Imperial War Museum) 出咗本書講參與過戰爭嘅動物俾小朋友，可以買俾仔女睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://shop.iwm.org.uk/images/product/Animal Heroes-1569941946.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fshop.iwm.org.uk%2Fimages%2Fproduct%2FAnimal%20Heroes-1569941946.jpg&h=d7108e3f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://shop.iwm.org.uk/p/27428/Tales-of-Amazing-Animal-Heroes\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fshop.iwm.org.uk%2Fp%2F27428%2FTales-of-Amazing-Animal-Heroes&d=PT6dGXJ5JuBAxmbDRmxpcHXW3JPDzH8o%2FFP8rJ6jlcg%3D&h=9d6ed25d\" target=\"_blank\">https://shop.iwm.org.uk/p/27428/Tales-of-Amazing-Animal-Heroes</a><br />\n封面隻貓就係嚟自香港嘅傳奇貓Simon 仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n之前開過Post 講佢嘅事跡<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n[香港之貓] 今日係 Simon the Cat 去彩虹橋嘅日子<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2303659\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2303659</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://www.warhistoryonline.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/12/Simon-with-crew-members-and-giant-pie.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.warhistoryonline.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2015%2F12%2FSimon-with-crew-members-and-giant-pie.jpg&h=d634df13&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://www.warhistoryonline.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/12/Simon-and-Lt-Cdr-Kerans-captain-of-HMS-Amethyst.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.warhistoryonline.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2015%2F12%2FSimon-and-Lt-Cdr-Kerans-captain-of-HMS-Amethyst.jpg&h=5bee008e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://www.thevintagenews.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/07/gettyimages-829787814-640x489.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thevintagenews.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2018%2F07%2Fgettyimages-829787814-640x489.jpg&h=b8141f98&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cattime.com/assets/uploads/2017/06/military-cats-2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcattime.com%2Fassets%2Fuploads%2F2017%2F06%2Fmilitary-cats-2.jpg&h=4c73e818&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.i-scmp.com/cdn-cgi/image/fit=contain,width=1098,format=auto/sites/default/files/styles/1200x800/public/images/methode/2017/10/13/488200ac-a1cb-11e7-84b5-dfc1701cb40c_1280x720_181227.JPG?itok=IFjlbdgt\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.i-scmp.com%2Fcdn-cgi%2Fimage%2Ffit%3Dcontain%2Cwidth%3D1098%2Cformat%3Dauto%2Fsites%2Fdefault%2Ffiles%2Fstyles%2F1200x800%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fmethode%2F2017%2F10%2F13%2F488200ac-a1cb-11e7-84b5-dfc1701cb40c_1280x720_181227.JPG%3Fitok%3DIFjlbdgt&h=d68dd080&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n雖然佢只係隻貓，但佢嘅故事都好值得傳頌落去<br />\n香港人同貓，都各自喺自己崗位為大英帝國付出<br />\n無論命定貓，都值得喺世界史留低美名<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0d7c98b18823a3f34ad5aca613a5499d87dee402","tid":2374430,"uid":43150,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-21T08:29:20.000Z","msg":"Simon 拎嘅係動物界維多利亞十字勳章<strong>Dickin Medal</strong> <br />\n而家係唯一嘅貓得主<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/stretching.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n如果想睇埋其他得主仲有其他書<br />\n佢嘅戰功比首相府嘅首席捕鼠大臣Larry絕不輸蝕<img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/swipe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/threat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://shop.iwm.org.uk/p/27285/The-Animal-Victoria-Cross---The-Dickin-Medal\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fshop.iwm.org.uk%2Fp%2F27285%2FThe-Animal-Victoria-Cross---The-Dickin-Medal&d=PT6dGXJ5JuBAxmbDRmxpcHXW3JPDzH8o%2FFP8rJ6jlcg%3D&h=50fae01f\" target=\"_blank\">https://shop.iwm.org.uk/p/27285/The-Animal-Victoria-Cross---The-Dickin-Medal</a>"},{"pid":"e4f6a09637550d6370f19b9571bf23da29612b3a","tid":2374430,"uid":259777,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-21T08:39:33.000Z","msg":"推，諗住買俾我姪女"},{"pid":"a114707c6d7faba6e8d29c7e023fa22a4b5cb907","tid":2374430,"uid":43150,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e4f6a09637550d6370f19b9571bf23da29612b3a","tid":2374430,"uid":259777,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-21T08:39:33.000Z","msg":"推，諗住買俾我姪女"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-21T08:42:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />好似可以網上訂，不過英國以外可以要預多少少時，一嚟脫歐之後有啲麻煩，二嚟武漢肺炎都會影響到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5421e5063eb35191f19de4f683dc72fa3b23c218","tid":2374430,"uid":43150,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-21T08:46:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/en/thumb/4/4a/Able_Seacat_Simon_(fair_use).jpg/220px-Able_Seacat_Simon_(fair_use).jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.wikimedia.org%2Fwikipedia%2Fen%2Fthumb%2F4%2F4a%2FAble_Seacat_Simon_%28fair_use%29.jpg%2F220px-Able_Seacat_Simon_%28fair_use%29.jpg&h=dabc9f04&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nSimon 雖然nominate 咗Dickin ，但其實未正式拎已經走咗，不過都無阻佢做貓得主<img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"beca9d38f5015b46f65d372ed75ac99c39735d2e","tid":2374430,"uid":20489,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-21T08:54:17.000Z","msg":"推<br />\n以前有睇過佢事蹟<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/point1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e2f276b0da44a606090919488aa2124c2957a82f","tid":2374430,"uid":19294,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-21T08:58:15.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"58fd5884e519149e794c8424d0668111529048e8","tid":2374430,"uid":43150,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"beca9d38f5015b46f65d372ed75ac99c39735d2e","tid":2374430,"uid":20489,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-21T08:54:17.000Z","msg":"推<br />\n以前有睇過佢事蹟<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/point1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-21T09:02:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />多啲宣揚俾人唔該<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我發覺身邊好多人唔識佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d91a72cb40509ea2afece1083f2153adb3cde9b1","tid":2374430,"uid":20489,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"58fd5884e519149e794c8424d0668111529048e8","tid":2374430,"uid":43150,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"beca9d38f5015b46f65d372ed75ac99c39735d2e","tid":2374430,"uid":20489,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-21T08:54:17.000Z","msg":"推<br />\n以前有睇過佢事蹟<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/point1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-21T09:02:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />多啲宣揚俾人唔該<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我發覺身邊好多人唔識佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-21T23:24:01.000Z","msg":"香港人無乜幾多個鐘意睇歷史<br />\nSimon 個故事好特別"},{"pid":"1c3e3900c93251b31710765aec9ee2e3c48d177f","tid":2374430,"uid":63017,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-22T01:21:57.000Z","msg":"根德中士就奮勇殺敵捨身成仁<br />\n佢就負責捉老鼠<br />\n竟然最後大家都可以拎同一級數既章"},{"pid":"9201e7e2a36b9e670937b6bb7da88f300bbe111b","tid":2374430,"uid":43150,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1c3e3900c93251b31710765aec9ee2e3c48d177f","tid":2374430,"uid":63017,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-22T01:21:57.000Z","msg":"根德中士就奮勇殺敵捨身成仁<br />\n佢就負責捉老鼠<br />\n竟然最後大家都可以拎同一級數既章"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-22T02:48:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我覺得Simon 仔都有大功，當時隻船好多老鼠，會污染啲食物，水<br />\n仲有隻船被困緊，士氣低落，但Simon都仍守住崗位，所以都值得啩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eac674b87048865b798187c467aa410415ff0f19","tid":2374430,"uid":43150,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d91a72cb40509ea2afece1083f2153adb3cde9b1","tid":2374430,"uid":20489,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"58fd5884e519149e794c8424d0668111529048e8","tid":2374430,"uid":43150,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"beca9d38f5015b46f65d372ed75ac99c39735d2e","tid":2374430,"uid":20489,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-21T08:54:17.000Z","msg":"推<br />\n以前有睇過佢事蹟<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/point1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-21T09:02:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />多啲宣揚俾人唔該<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我發覺身邊好多人唔識佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-21T23:24:01.000Z","msg":"香港人無乜幾多個鐘意睇歷史<br />\nSimon 個故事好特別"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-22T02:52:36.000Z","msg":"<